Titolo: Cricket Revolution

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Cricket Revolution is a sports multiplayer video game developed by Mindstorm Studios, based on the sport of cricket. The game focuses on an online community system serving detailed cricket stats for gamers through internet play in addition to a LAN based and offline component. It is the first ever video game developed by Pakistan to land on Steam.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: N/A
